    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Escort Ship\nApproval code: = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nA group of ships located at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> are requesting an escort. If you accept, head to the location immediately and await instructions. The client claims that this escort is purely a precautionary measure, but that doesn\u2019t mean you should drop your guard. Expect some hostile forces and deal with them appropriately.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Eckhart_EscortShips_E_desc",
